ord":"great","count":1},{"word":"show","count":1},{"word":"i've","count":1},{"word":"collected","count":1},{"word":"next","count":1},{"word":"universe","count":1},{"word":"secrets","count":1},{"word":"hiding","count":1},{"word":"beyond","count":1},{"word":"infinite","count":1},{"word":"stars","count":1},{"word":"anyway","count":1},{"word":"short","count":1},{"word":"came","count":1},{"word":"fallen","count":1},{"word":"instrument","count":1},{"word":"shows","count":1},{"word":"high","count":1},{"word":"chance","count":1},{"word":"close","count":1},{"word":"eh","count":1},{"word":"knew","count":1},{"word":"undiscovered","count":1},{"word":"area","count":1},{"word":"must've","count":1},{"word":"sealed","count":1},{"word":"ice","count":1},{"word":"wall","count":1},{"word":"ah","count":1},{"word":"fault","count":1},{"word":"putting","count":1},{"word":"everyone","count":1},{"word":"danger","count":1},{"word":"mmm","count":1},{"word":"agree","count":1},{"word":"inside","count":1},{"word":"o-okay","count":1},{"word":"t-this","count":1},{"word":"section","count":1},{"word":"describes","count":1},{"word":"used","count":1},{"word":"greatsword","count":1},{"word":"seal","count":1},{"word":"behind","count":1},{"word":"href","count":1},{"word":"travelled","count":1},{"word":"reach","count":1},{"word":"lahai-roi","count":1},{"word":"battle","count":1},{"word":"fierce","count":1},{"word":"pushed","count":1},{"word":"brink","count":1},{"word":"defeat","count":1},{"word":"moment","count":1},{"word":"reasons","count":1},{"word":"unknown","count":1},{"word":"exostrider's","count":1},{"word":"reactor","count":1},{"word":"drive","count":1},{"word":"flared","count":1},{"word":"blinding","count":1},{"word":"light","count":1},{"word":"sigrika","count":1},{"word":"library","count":1},{"word":"hmm","count":1},{"word":"huh","count":1},{"word":"ugh","count":1},{"word":"hurts","count":1},{"word":"collapsed","count":1},{"word":"entry","count":1},{"word":"point","count":1},{"word":"blocked","count":1},{"word":"kind","count":1},{"word":"barrier","count":1},{"word":"caused","count":1},{"word":"unstable","count":1},{"word":"frequencies","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Hm? Y-you are the one who was talking to yourself in class…","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Oh, and Dr. Herssen! You are... traveling together? Did the Academy greenlight a new field trip?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Yes! Exactly. I-I heard the frostlands have been experiencing changes since Helios was launched… I had a hypothesis that new debris fields might have been exposed!","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Space equipment that fell from the sky long ago! Probes, satellites, and even space stations…!","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Some previous digs unearthed wreckage containing records lost during the Lament.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Oh, and images! Photos taken in orbit of other planets! They were absolutely… breathtakingly beautiful!!","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Huff... Huff. Oh, sorry, I-I got carried away...","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Thank you… Sometimes, I'll just start info-dumping... I know it's not the best…","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Really?! That's great! I'll... I'll show you the data I've collected next time we're in class!","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"The universe… What secrets is it hiding beyond all those infinite stars?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"I really want to know.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Anyway, in short, I came here for the fallen debris.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"The data on the instrument shows there's a high chance that close by… Eh?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"I knew it! There had to have been undiscovered debris in this area!","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"It must've been sealed in the ice wall all this time…","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Ah! I'm so sorry... It's my fault for putting everyone in danger...","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Mmm...","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"I-I agree! I want to see what's inside too...","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"O-okay. T-this section...  it describes how the Exostrider used its greatsword to seal the Threnodian behind the <te href=750036>Stridergate</te>.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"The records say both the Exostrider and the Threnodian travelled through the Stridergate to reach Lahai-Roi. Their battle was fierce.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"The Threnodian pushed the Exostrider to the brink of defeat.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"But at that moment, for reasons unknown, the Exostrider's Reactor Drive flared with blinding light—","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Sigrika, could you come to the library with me?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Hmm—","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"...Huh?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Ugh! That hurts...","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"There's a collapsed entry point over there, but… it's blocked. Some kind of barrier caused by unstable frequencies.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001}]}